(318, '_site_transient_fusion_wordpress_org_plugins', 'a:5:{s:11:\"woocommerce\";a:25:{s:4:\"name\";s:11:\"WooCommerce\";s:4:\"slug\";s:11:\"woocommerce\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"3.4.5\";s:6:\"author\";s:48:\"<a href=\"https://woocommerce.com\">Automattic</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:40:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/woothemes\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.7\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"4.9.8\";s:12:\"requires_php\";b:0;s:13:\"compatibility\";a:0:{}s:6:\"rating\";d:92;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:2506;i:4;i:118;i:3;i:63;i:2;i:64;i:1;i:197;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:2948;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:1250;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:1148;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:51513867;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2018-08-29 6:46pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2011-09-27\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:24:\"https://woocommerce.com/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:7347:\"<p>WooCommerce je besplatan eCommerce plugin koji vam omogućuje da prodajete bilo što. Izgrađen da se neprimjetno integrira u WordPress, WooCommerce je omiljena svjetska eCommerce solucija koja vlasnicima trgovina i developerima pruža potpunu kontrolu.</p>\n<p>Beskonačno fleksibilan, uz stotine besplatnih i premium dodataka, WooCommerce sada pogoni 30% svih online trgovina &#8211; više nego bilo koja druga platforma.</p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'390\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/1KahlicghaE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></span>\n<h4>Prodajte bilo što, bilo gdje.</h4>\n<p>S WooCommerce, možete prodavati fizičke i digitalne proizvode svih oblika i veličina, u raznim varijacima, višestrukim konfiguracijama, instant preuzimanja za kupce, čak i prodavati affiliate proizvode iz raznih online trgovina.</p>\n<p>S premium ekstenzijama, možete ponuditi rezervacije, članstava, i ponavljajućih pretplate. Možda želite prodavati mjesečne pretplate za fizičke proizvode, ili ponuditi svojim članovima popust na digitalni download ? Sve je moguće.</p>\n<h4>Dostavite gdje god želite.</h4>\n<p>Ponudite besplatnu dostavu, fiksnu cijenu dostave , ili napravite izračune u stvarnom vremenu. Ograničite svoje pošiljke na određene zemlje ili otvorite svoj ​​dućan cijelom svijetu. Dostava je vrlo konfigurabilna, a WooCommerce podržava čak &#8220;drop shipping&#8221;.</p>\n<h4>Opsežne opcije plaćanja</h4>\n<p>WooCommerce dolazi u paketu sa opcijama za prihvat popularnih kreditnih kartica, PayPal-a, bankovne transfere i plaćanje pouzećem . Trebate dodatne opcije ? Više od 140 payment gatewaya specifičnih za regije može se integrirati u WooCommerce , uključujući i popularne izbore kao Stripe, Authorize.Net i Amazon plaćanja .</p>\n<h4>Vi sve kontrolirate &#8212; zauvijek</h4>\n<p>WooCommerce vam daje potpunu kontrolu nad vašom trgovinom, od poreza, razine zaliha do računa korisnika .Dodavajte ili uklanjajte ekstenzije , promijenite dizajn, promijenite postavke kako želite. Sve je pod vašom kontrolom.</p>\n<p>Jedan od najvećih rizika korištenja hostanih eCommerce platforma je ono što se događa vašoj trgovini ako pružatelj usluge zatvori dućan . Uz WooCommerce, imate potpunu kontrolu, tako da nema razloga za zabrinutost. Vaši podaci pripadaju vama &#8211; i sigurni su!</p>\n<h4>Definirajte svoj style sa Storefront temom</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/storefront/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Storefront</a> is a free WordPress theme available to any WooCommerce store. Along with deep WooCommerce integration, Storefront prioritizes speed and uptime while eliminating theme and plugin conflicts during major updates.</p>\n<p>Prilagodite izgled Storefront teme vašim željama definirajući svoje ​​stilove ili odabirom jedne od nekoliko <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/product-category/themes/storefront-child-theme-themes/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Storefront child tema</a>. Odabir je na vama i sve je open source.</p>\n<h4>Izgrađen s developerima na umu</h4>\n<p>Proširivo, prilagodljivo i open source &#8211; WooCommerce je stvoren s programerima na umu. Sa svojim snažnim , robusnim frameworkom, možete skalirati trgovinu svog klijenta, od osnovnih do vrlo kompleksnih trgovina.</p>\n<p>Izgrađen pmoću REST API-a, WooCommerce se može integrirati u bilo koju uslugu . Podacima vaše trgovine se može pristupiti bilo gdje, bilo kada, na 100% siguran način. WooCommerce omogućuje programerima lako stvaranje, izmjenu , i rast trgovine koja ispunjava njihove specifikacije .</p>\n<p>Bez obzira na veličinu trgovine koju želite napraviti, WooCommerce se može skalirati kako bi  zadovoljio vaše potrebe. Uz sve veću zbirku od više od 300 ekstenzija , možete poboljšati funkcionalnosti svake trgovine  &#8211; ili čak napraviti svoje vlastiti rješenje.</p>\n<p>Ako je zabrinuti zbog sigurnosti, ne brinite. WooCommerce je revidiran od strane dediciranog tima programera koji rade danonoćno kako bi identificirati i zakrpali sve otkrivene greške .</p>\n<p>Također podupiremo WooCommerce i sve njegove dodatke pomoću sveobuhvatne , lako dostupne dokumentacije . Uz naše dokumente, možete naučiti kako stvoriti trgovinu sukladno željama vaših klijenata.</p>\n<h4>Izobilje proširenja</h4>\n<p>WordPress.org je dom vrhunskih dodataka za WooCommerce, uključujući :</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-google-analytics-integration/\">Google Analytics</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-delivery-notes/\">Delivery Notes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-pdf-invoices-packing-slips/\">PDF Invoices and Packing Slips</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/affiliates-woocommerce-light/\">Affiliates Integration Light</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-new-product-badge/\">New Product Badges</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Želite ih vidjeti sve? Pretražite WordPress.org koristeći pojam ‘WooCommerce’.</p>\n<p>Ako ste u potrazi za nečim što su odobrili i održavaju programeri koji su izgradili WooCommerce , postoji mnoštvo vrhunskih eCommerce nastavaka, od kojih najpoznatiji uključuju :</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-subscriptions/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce Subscriptions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-memberships/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce Memberships</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-bookings/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce Bookings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/dynamic-pricing/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dynamic Pricing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/table-rate-shipping/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Table Rate Shipping</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/product-csv-import-suite/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Product CSV Import Suite</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ima toga još. Posjetite našu <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/product-category/woocommerce-extensions/\" rel=\"nofollow\">stranicu s dodacima</a> kako bi saznali što sve možete učiniti pomoću premium WooCommerce dodataka.</p>\n<h4>Pridružite se našoj rastućoj zajednici</h4>\n<p>Kada preuzmete WooCommerce, pridružujete se zajednici vlasnika više od milijun trgovina, programera, i WordPress entuzijasta. Mi smo jedna od najbrže rastućih open source zajednica na internetu, i neovisno o vašoj vještini, voljeli bismo da nam se pridružite!</p>\n<p>Ako želite doprinijeti WooCommerceu, imamo više od 350 suradnika , a uvijek ima mjesta za još. Posjetite<a href=\"https://github.com/woocommerce/woocommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce GitHub Repozitorij</a> i saznajte kako pripomoći.</p>\n<p>Želite dodati novi jezik u WooCommerce? Odlično ! Možete doprinjeti preko <a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/projects/wp-plugins/woocommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">translate.wordpress.org</a>.</p>\n<p>I, za kraj, razmislite o sudjelovanju ili organizaciji WooCommerce Meetup na lokalnoj razini. Više o toj temi <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/woocommerce/meetups/\" rel=\"nofollow\">ovdje</a>.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:2345:\"<h4>Minimalni zahtjevi</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>PHP version 5.2.4 or greater (PHP 5.6 or greater is recommended)</li>\n<li>MySQL version 5.0 or greater (MySQL 5.6 or greater is recommended)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Visit the <a href=\"https://docs.woocommerce.com/document/server-requirements/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce server requirements documentation</a> for a detailed list of server requirements.</p>\n<h4>Automatska instalacija</h4>\n<p>Automatska instalacija je najjednostavnija opcija, s obzirom da WordPress odrađuje prijenos datoteka , a vi ne morate napustiti svoj ​​web preglednik. Da bi automatski instalirali WooCommerce , prijavite se u WordPress nadzornu ploču , idite na Izbornik dodataka i kliknite Dodaj novo .</p>\n<p>U polju za pretraživanje upišite &#8221; WooCommerce &#8221; i kliknite na Pretraži dodatke . Nakon što ste pronašli naš eCommerce plugin možete pogledati detalje o njemu , kao što su dnevnik promjena, ocjene i opis. Ono što je najvažnije, možete ga instalirati jednostavnim klikom na &#8221; Install Now&#8221;.</p>\n<h4>Ručna instalacija</h4>\n<p>Metoda ručne instalacije uključuje skidanje našeg eCommerce dodatka i uploadanje na svoj web poslužitelj putem svoje omiljene FTP aplikacije. WordPress codex sadrži <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Managing_Plugins#Manual_Plugin_Installation\" rel=\"nofollow\">uputstva kako to učiniti ovdje</a>.</p>\n<h4>Ažuriranje</h4>\n<p>Automatsko ažuriranje bi trebalo raditi bez problema; no, mudro je prethodno napraviti backup vaše stranice, za svaki slučaj,</p>\n<p>Ako nekim slučajem nakon nadogradnje imate problema sa stranicama trgovine/kategorija, samo trebate ponovo snimiti Stalne veze proizvoda i to na način da odete na WordPress &gt; Postavke &gt; Stalne veze i kliknete &#8220;Spremi&#8221;. Nakon toga bi se sve trebalo normalizirati.</p>\n<h4>Sample data</h4>\n<p>WooCommerce comes with some sample data you can use to see how products look; import sample_products.xml via the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-importer/\">WordPress importer</a>. You can also use the core <a href=\"https://docs.woocommerce.com/document/product-csv-importer-exporter/\" rel=\"nofollow\">CSV importer</a> or our <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/product-csv-import-suite/\" rel=\"nofollow\">CSV Import Suite plugin</a> to import sample_products.csv.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:2341:\"\n<h4>Gdje mogu pronaći WooCommerce dokumentaciju i korisničke upute?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Za pomoć pri postavljanju i konfiguriranju WooCommercea pogledajte naš <a href=\"https://docs.woocommerce.com/documentation/plugins/woocommerce/getting-started/\" rel=\"nofollow\">korisnički priručnik</a></p>\n<p>Za dodavanje funkcionalnosti ili kreiranje tema za WooCommerce, pročitajte naš <a href=\"https://docs.woocommerce.com/documentation/plugins/woocommerce/woocommerce-codex/\" rel=\"nofollow\">codex</a>.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Gdje se obratiti za korisničku podršku ili razgovarati s drugim korisnicima?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Ako zapnete, potražite pomoć u <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/woocommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce Plugin Forumu</a>.</p>\n<p>For help with premium extensions from WooCommerce.com, use <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/my-account/tickets/\" rel=\"nofollow\">our helpdesk</a>.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Hoće li WooCommerce raditi s mojom temom?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Da; WooCommerce će raditi sa bilo kojom temom, ali možda će trebati dodati stilove kako bi izgledale skladno. Molimo, pogledajte naš <a href=\"https://docs.woocommerce.com/documentation/plugins/woocommerce/woocommerce-codex/\" rel=\"nofollow\">codex</a> za pomoć. Ako tražite temu s integriranom podrškom za WooCommerce, preporučujemo <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/storefront/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Storefront</a>.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Gdje mogu zatražiti nove funkcionalnosti, eCommerce teme i pluginove?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Možete glasati i zatražiti nove značajke i proširenja u našem <a href=\"http://ideas.woocommerce.com/forums/133476-woocommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooIdeas boardu</a></p>\n</p>\n<h4>Gdje mogu prijaviti bugove ili doprinjeti projektu?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Bugove možete prijaviti na našem forumu za podršku, ili još bolje na  <a href=\"https://github.com/woocommerce/woocommerce/issues\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce GitHub repozitoriju</a>.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Gdje mogu pronaći dokumentaciju o REST API-u?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Dokumentaciju o našem REST API-u možete pronaći na <a href=\"https://woocommerce.github.io/woocommerce-rest-api-docs/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce REST API Docs</a>.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>WooCommerce je mrak! Kako mogu doprinijeti?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes you can! Join in on our <a href=\"https://github.com/woocommerce/woocommerce/\" rel=\"nofollow\">GitHub repository</a> 🙂</p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:30555:\"<h4>3.4.5 &#8211; 2018-08-29</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Tweak sanitization when resetting password cookie. #20901</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Use <code>+</code> instead of <code>array_merge</code> when appending parent to tax class to fix issues with numeric tax class names. #20916</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Correct translation for North Khorasan. #20972</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Unify scroll-to notices for all browsers. #20992</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Prevent multiple slashing of variation&#8217;s SKU. #21019</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Variation image in fullscreen now shows correct caption for the respective image. #21022</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Vertically center admin order action buttons. #21053</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Correct context for shipping packages translation. #21065</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Add permission checks for installing Jetpack on the setup wizard. #21072</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Use refund currency instead of store default currency when displaying refund amount in the edit order screen. #21106</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Fix a typo in REST API customer schema. #21171</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Use entire sentence for checkout address_2 placeholder string. #21186</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Only suppress comments number on unsupported theme shop page. #21191</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Don&#8217;t allow users without manage_product_terms permissions to create categories using the product importer. #21192</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Correct sale coupon restriction logic. #21219</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3.4.4 &#8211; 2018-07-25</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Only wordwrap plain email content. #20723</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Better escaping on product quick edit. #20740</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Log file deletion. #20730</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Search feature in Webhooks and REST API keys settings. #20706</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Notices in REST API keys settings screen. #20706</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; add a check to prevent WC_Geolite_Integration::get_country_iso() from generating a PHP undefined index notice when unable to determine the country code for a given IP address. #20608</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Variable product stock display if parent is stock managed and not the variation. #20661</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Correctly hide cost for zero cost shipping methods after placing orders. #20663</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Disabled autocomplete to prevent datepicker overlapping. #20687</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Prevent a PHP notice in the setup wizard when store state is not selectable. #20695</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Fix logic error in WC_Product_CSV_Exporter::get_column_value_stock. #20753</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Fixed missing notice about no product variation matching. #20762</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Correct PHPDocs in exporter class. #20861</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Prevent Mailchimp redirection during the Setup Wizard. #20879</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Don&#8217;t hide coupon form after coupon has been applied. #20889</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; Remove (optional) text from Address line 2 field. #20622 #20639</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; Removed 100% width for images on single product page using 2017 theme. #20818</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; Add margin to best selling product title in the dashboard widget to avoid overlapping the sparkline. #20849</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; Re-add woocommerce_order_details_after_customer_details_filter removed during WC 3.2. #20886</li>\n<li>Dev &#8211; Added woocommerce_calculate_item_totals_taxes filter. #20586</li>\n<li>Dev &#8211; Links to next and previous page sent out in HTTP header via REST API fixed for some endpoints. #20686</li>\n<li>Dev &#8211; Better wc_format_phone_number cleaning. #20637</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3.4.3 &#8211; 2018-06-20</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Fix label for the price filter widget on RTL sites. #20417</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Checkout: stopPropagation when payment method selected so description tips show on radio buttons. #20432</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Shipping zone settings: fixed title for shipping methods without settings. #20441</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Ensure custom Webhook topic selections are correctly saved in admin. #20406</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Webhook bottom bulk actions. #20445</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Fixes multisite orders dashboard widget to use order number rather than ID. #20457</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Add check to ensure download log FK does not exist before adding it. Update routine will cleanup any duplicates. #20478</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; IPv6 support with HTTP_X_FORWARDED_FOR header. #20479</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Avoid setting wrong prices when syncing grouped products with children. #20482</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Separation of explode and end functions in two lines. End function should get a reference as parameter. #20500</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Initialize payment gateways before running bulk actions so gateways can listen for events. #20502</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Cast shipping total to a float so incl. tax shows only when needed. #20531</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Fix automatic stock status updates based on stock level. #20573</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Improved sanitize_special_column_name_regex trim to fix column matching when importing CSVs. #20486</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Force importer log table to wrap long columns. #20534</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Rest API: Prevent errors if variation parent is invalid and cannot be read. #20572</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Rest API: Remove legacy API enabled check from auth endpoint. #20499</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Display products on sub-subcategories when sorting parent category by price. #20579</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Set order status to refunded when a PayPal transaction is refunded. #20574</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; fix undefined index in abstract-wc-widget. #20544</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Round items for order total when recalculating order values to match cart. #20533</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Removed mysql transactions when updating order status, tweaked caching, and improved version transient cleanup to prevent possible deadlocks on checkout. #20537</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; Added a message to promote Wootenberg when running Gutenberg feature plugin. #20524</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; Added a warning notice before removing personal data from orders in bulk. #20481</li>\n<li>Dev &#8211; generate_select_html and generate_multiselect_html functions again support the usage of integer-keyed arrays as available values. #20569</li>\n<li>Dev &#8211; Allow order billing fields to use a provided &#8216;value&#8217;. #20424</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3.4.2 &#8211; 2018-06-05</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Flexslider gallery fixes for RTL sites, and for variation image switching. #20328 #20321</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Allow forms to be submitted when the password strength library fails to load. #20362</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Personal data exporter: Do not export a customer data group containing no data. #20347</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Fix navigation notification in settings when clicking save. #20335</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Show discount amount for free shipping coupons. #20334</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Fixed cache clearing for category children for sites running object caching. #20308</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Use correct escaping on select2 placeholders. #20364</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Order by price clauses when searching within terms. #20391</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Clear needs_processing transient when adding a product to an order. #20390</li>\n<li>Enhancement &#8211; Permission_id constraint checks on install. #20366</li>\n<li>Dev &#8211; Added order to &#8220;woocommerce_order_is_vat_exempt&#8221; filter arguments. #20365</li>\n<li>Localization &#8211; Disable states for Bahrain. #20363</li>\n<li>Localization &#8211; Disable states for Luxemberg. #20389</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3.4.1 &#8211; 2018-05-29</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Fix webhook admin filtering URLs. #20236</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Add missing wp_unslash calls to product data meta box to prevent quote characters being escaped on save. #20235</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Display price filter widget in LTR mode on RTL sites. #20221</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Refactor WC_Coupon constructor to allow for passing in coupon objects. #20193</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Path field in advanced CSV importer was broken due to an esc_url call. #20191</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Prevent shipping method instances trying to save settings on non-instance screens. #20217</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Wrapper function to get full mysql version string with mariadb handling. #20231</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; woocommerce_pagination had some extra white space. #20214</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; If a file size cannot be read, ignore range headers to prevent offsite downloads being 0kb. #20205</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Allow HTML when using <code>wc_attribute_label()</code>. #20202</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Update address-i18n.js to prevent appending multiple &#8220;(optional)&#8221; labels. #20195</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Check plugin properties exist when listening to auto_update_plugin hook. #20234</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Add extra checks in <code>get_canonical_package_rate_ids</code> to prevent notices. #20237</li>\n<li>Fix &#8